{"tid":2198416,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"竹君：張宇人沒有普通常識","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T11:01:11.000Z","uid":250775,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33a2db34d8ba4bc82a18125a7268afb81052c600","tid":2198416,"uid":250775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"張竹君：戴口罩時不接觸口罩表面是普通常識<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，就戴口罩問題，自己並非專家，應詢問感染控制專家意見。但她說，戴口罩時不應接觸口罩表面、或接觸口罩前後需要洗手，這都是普通常識。當局放寬措施，酒吧業表示會要求客人飲酒時才拉低口罩，飲完聊天時就馬上戴好口罩，張竹君早前被問到有關做法時指出，不斷拉低口罩飲酒的做法，比不戴口罩更高危，身兼行政會議成員的飲食界立法會議員張宇人，其後不點名批評，指「大家不要扮專家」。<br />\n<br />\nSource: RTHK 2020-09-11 17:36:10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">撐竹君，人哥咪扮專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6053824bfb5b4b47a469e87ea6139ae35a276238","tid":2198416,"uid":250775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f08563fe1d7bd56b36d56b5009a14de1a7b53d","tid":2198416,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"已正評"},{"pid":"f0e5b429ffef906c944925806a7888f8c728a1b3","tid":2198416,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"撐20蚊張對家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1614a904f49b9b92354afbd29364365fbf2629","tid":2198416,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b7ccb6b34aba7c4240d8455548ead3835b2151ac","tid":2198416,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"廿蚊張用廿蚊當口罩用啦屌"}]}